.SS "\fBSoSFVec3f\fP SoPointLightDragger::translation"
This field is continuously updated to contain the translation of the pointlight dragger\&. The application programmer will typically connect this to the \fBSoPointLight::location\fP field of a \fBSoPointLight\fP node (unless using the \fBSoPointLightManip\fP class, where this is taken care of automatically)\&.
.PP
It may also of course be connected to any other location / translation field controlling the position of scenegraph geometry, it does not have to part of a \fBSoPointLight\fP node specifically\&. 

